          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Unacceptable behaviors include: use of sexualized and violent language or imagery; disruption, incitement, rumor-making, insulting, derogatory comments, and personal and political attacks; public or private harassment to participants; publishing others' information such as physical and email addresses without their explicit authorization; and other conduct that can reasonably be considered a violation of this Code of Conduct."
