              "name": "Ensure required files are available",
              "text": "Before verifying, ensure both the image file openEuler-24.03-LTS-raspi-aarch64.img.xz and the verification file openEuler-24.03-LTS-raspi-aarch64.img.xz.sha256sum are available locally.",
              "url": "https://www.openeuler.openatom.cn/en/wiki/install/raspberry-pi#verifying-the-image-integrity"
